The time has come! 

After 4 months of honest ground work, creating a platform for change, supporting thousands, the @shikhardhawan.foundation is now Officially Launching by opening applications for adoption of 11 NGOs!✅🤝

If you are an organisation or are working towards a cause which can benefit the society, fill out the Impact 11 form through our website and let’s create change together!✨

The Website, www.shikhardhawanfoundation.com, is now live, link in bio! 
Thank you for the endless love and support, we promise to continue working and giving back to the society❤️

#RiseWithSDF #UpwardsAndOnwards #ShikharDhawanFoundation #ShikharDhawan #NGO #NGOIndia
